From: Dedy Lansky <dlansky@codeaurora.org>
Date: Sun, 29 Jul 2018 14:59:16 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] cfg80211/mac80211: make ieee80211_send_layer2_update a public
 function
Patch-mainline: v4.20-rc1
Git-commit: 30ca1aa536211f5ac3de0173513a7a99a98a97f3
References: bsc#1159912 CVE-2019-5108

Make ieee80211_send_layer2_update() a common function so other drivers
can re-use it.

Signed-off-by: Dedy Lansky <dlansky@codeaurora.org>
Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Acked-by: Cho, Yu-Chen <acho@suse.com>
---
 include/net/cfg80211.h |   11 +++++++++++
 net/mac80211/cfg.c     |   48 ++----------------------------------------------
 net/wireless/util.c    |   47 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 60 insertions(+), 46 deletions(-)

--- a/include/net/cfg80211.h
+++ b/include/net/cfg80211.h
@@ -2268,6 +2268,17 @@ unsigned int cfg80211_classify8021d(stru
 const u8 *cfg80211_find_ie(u8 eid, const u8 *ies, int len);
 
 /**
+ * cfg80211_send_layer2_update - send layer 2 update frame
+ *
+ * @dev: network device
+ * @addr: STA MAC address
+ *
+ * Wireless drivers can use this function to update forwarding tables in bridge
+ * devices upon STA association.
+ */
+void cfg80211_send_layer2_update(struct net_device *dev, const u8 *addr);
+
